@RichardKyire 
cnpm will do. so you should use `npm install`.
if you failed for the sake of poor network, u better use a proxy, especially in China.

@RichardKyire 
the dependencies can be set  in  ` ./superset/assets/package.json`.
better not change the default dependency version.
read [this](https://github.com/apache/incubator-superset/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md) setup guide carefully.
 try `yarn install`  again and again, u will make it sometime :flushed:
